
{{alias}}( x )
    Copies the elements of an indexed array-like object to a new "generic"
    array.

    Parameters
    ----------
    x: ArrayLikeObject
        Input array.

    Returns
    -------
    out: Array
        Output array.

    Examples
    --------
    > var out = {{alias}}( [ 1, 2, 3 ] )
